                    p We offer you daily practice sessions at hours of your choosing.   
        div.card 
            h3 PROVIDE A CERTIFICATE
            div.card-box 
                div.card-img
                    img(src="/static/image/02.png", alt="daily practice")
                div.card-content 
                    p We provide you with an accredited certificate.  
        div.card 
            h3 EXPERT TEACHERS
            div.card-box 
                div.card-img
                    img(src="/static/image/03.png", alt="daily practice")
                div.card-content 
                    p We offer instruction from highly skilled and experienced teachers.          
    section#sponsorsection
